description:
Who can turn their restaurant dream into a reality?

Five teams from around Australia, all with an idea for a new restaurant, have been given the chance to live their dream. But can they turn their dream into a money-making reality?

Restaurant Revolution is a new multi-night reality show which sees ordinary Australians charged with designing and running their own pop-up restaurant.




Restaurant Revolution - Season 1, Episode 1


Premiere

The five teams' restaurants are introduced in major capital cities around Australia. In their first challenge, teams pitch their restaurant concept, food and vision to the expert panel to earn the first share of funds. $100,000 was the total prize pool distributed among the teams based on their efforts for their pitch from best to worst.



Original Air Date: 28-Jul-2015
